{"tid":844042,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"秋冬離不開蛇9兩大滋補食材","createTime":"2018-10-01T14:34:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T06:24:04.000Z","uid":22589,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2cf61300ba31ea7dce4229d20d2ee769f693e444","tid":844042,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T14:34:59.000Z","msg":"諗起心郁郁"},{"pid":"51ee48fef6084b0741ef5264019fdfe451396444","tid":844042,"uid":12498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T14:36:55.000Z","msg":"狗肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fe8c1a6cd65ffb229bc2ff489b8b28090b0b5d5","tid":844042,"uid":47268,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T14:37:20.000Z","msg":"即刻落街捉隻過下口癮先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90a36f24e3f902d5ecb2879cb2255daffdb23bd2","tid":844042,"uid":3014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T14:39:06.000Z","msg":"Cos<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6920a96494727b0de9b43a49256858d68c12fb4","tid":844042,"uid":44285,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4fe8c1a6cd65ffb229bc2ff489b8b28090b0b5d5","tid":844042,"uid":47268,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T14:37:20.000Z","msg":"即刻落街捉隻過下口癮先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T14:39:18.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗？"},{"pid":"3b1de1ac36038727b7f49ec152aa4ef052c021f3","tid":844042,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T14:39:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.tvbs.com.tw/world/942660\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvbs.com.tw%2Fworld%2F942660&d=9MYsJ7ZD%2B279ssC7TQbG%2BI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=876eb24b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.tvbs.com.tw/world/942660</a><br />\n大陸廣西玉林知名的狗肉節昨(21日)登場，雖然吃狗肉為當地風俗民情，但仍引發許多爭議！儘管當地官方和部分民間人士否認狗肉節的存在，但近日卻有許多外地人湧入玉林吃狗，且店內座無虛席。<br />\n<br />\n玉林狗肉節上千隻狗兒被賣入市場，遭到支解懸吊，不少店家競相叫價拍賣，因此狗肉節引起國際間愛狗人士的撻伐，但對於當地人來說，吃狗肉已經成了文化與飲食習慣，且賣狗肉還是當地居民收入來源之一；據《梨視頻》報導，有當地民眾表示只要沒錢用就會拿出來賣，他們也相當無奈地說「<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">感情能當飯吃</span>嗎？<br />\n</span>」<br />\n隨著時代的推進，大陸各地反狗肉的聲浪愈來愈高漲，在輿論壓力下，玉林狗肉節的舉辦也愈加艱困，遊客量減少，由於狗肉所影響的層面複雜，這也是對人文背景不同理解所產生的落差，因此想要改變當地居民根深蒂固的思維，恐怕還需要一段時間的等待。"},{"pid":"0882e0e81eafefcfa149439f87f6c93ab842e76b","tid":844042,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90a36f24e3f902d5ecb2879cb2255daffdb23bd2","tid":844042,"uid":3014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T14:39:06.000Z","msg":"Cos<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T14:45:55.000Z","msg":"無人性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00b6fcea434cece5a685483e29dbb9ca0293ec6f","tid":844042,"uid":22589,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e6920a96494727b0de9b43a49256858d68c12fb4","tid":844042,"uid":44285,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4fe8c1a6cd65ffb229bc2ff489b8b28090b0b5d5","tid":844042,"uid":47268,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T14:37:20.000Z","msg":"即刻落街捉隻過下口癮先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T14:39:18.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T14:46:26.000Z","msg":"波台得肉酸先係狗"},{"pid":"093eb700f043dbec4e620cb9a8c97702ded25f02","tid":844042,"uid":44285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00b6fcea434cece5a685483e29dbb9ca0293ec6f","tid":844042,"uid":22589,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e6920a96494727b0de9b43a49256858d68c12fb4","tid":844042,"uid":44285,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4fe8c1a6cd65ffb229bc2ff489b8b28090b0b5d5","tid":844042,"uid":47268,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score"